text: Rancenay is a commune in the Doubs department. It is in the Bourgogne-Franche- Comté region in eastern France. ==Geography== The commune is northeast of Boussières. It is split by the river Doubs. ==Population== ==Related pages== * Communes of the Doubs department ==References== ==Other websites== * Rancenay on the intercommunal Web site of the department Category:Communes in Doubs
